high_descs: Turn around, walk towards the sinks, hang a left at the sinks, and face the waste basket that's on the floor and to the left of the toilet.
Pick up the lip stick that's on the floor and to the left of the green waste basket.
Walk to the cabinet below the left sink and all the way to the left.
Open the cabinet door, place the lip stick inside of the cabinet on the left front edge, and close the door.
Face the area between the toilet and the sinks with the toilet brush and plunger.
Pick up the toilet paper roll from the back of the toilet and to the right of the spray bottle.
Walk to the cabinet below the left sink and all the way to the left.
Open the left side cabinet door below the left sink, place the toilet paper roll behind the tube of lip stick in the cabinet, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: To put a tube of lip stick, and a roll of toilet paper in the cabinet below the left sink.

high_descs: Move to the toilet facing the wall to the left of the sinks
Pick up toilet roll from the bin
Move the the front of the toilet to the left of the sink
Put the roll in the cabinet closest to the toilet
Move to the toilet ahead of you
Pick up the toilet paper from the toilet
Move the the front of the toilet to the left of the sink
Put the roll in the cabinet closest to the toilet
anns.task_desc: Put two rolls of toilet paper in the cabinet closest to the toilet.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the tube on the ground next to the green trash can.
Pick up the tube on the ground.
Turn around and walk to the cabinet below the sink on the left.
Place the tube in the leftmost cabinet below the sink.
Walk to the toilet paper roll on the back of the toilet.
Pick up the toilet paper roll from the back of the toilet.
Step back and walk to the cabinets below the left sink.
Place the roll of toilet paper in the leftmost cabinet below the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a tube and a roll of toilet paper in the leftmost cabinet below the sink.
